# qb-linq (project)

- **Library:** Header-only C++17, `namespace qb::linq`. Public include: **`<qb/linq.h>`** only.
- **Before edits:** **`AGENTS.md`**, **`docs/BUILDING.md`** (CMake facts), **`docs/LLM_CONTEXT.md`** (implementation map).
- **CRTP:** Algorithms live on `detail::query_range_algorithms<Derived, Iter>`; implementations call `derived().begin()` / `end()`.
- **Verify:** Build **`qb_linq_tests`** and run **`ctest`** when possible; preserve **`qb_linq_benchmark`** build if benchmarks touched. User-visible changes: **`CHANGELOG.md`** (`[Unreleased]`) per **`CONTRIBUTING.md`**.
- **Scope:** Minimal, focused diffs; match surrounding style and Doxygen; do not expand scope beyond the task.
